f-23_"><p class="sc-bJBfJu eVDjFe pf-24_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bOQUxc quwHz pf-26_">Image by nazariykarkhut via Envato Elements</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-e079" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fsvrPk eTuePL pf-27_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-eNSrbD jPuwGZ"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-28_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-29_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-30_">The importance of an effective Core Skills Training Framework in UK healthcare</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-32_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-79319400-5b48-49b8-8d2c-64c077b19fb4"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">In the dynamic and demanding healthcare landscape, ensuring that staff are equipped with the right skills and knowledge is not just important - it’s essential. The Core Skills Training Framework (CSTF) has emerged as a trusted benchmark for statutory and mandatory training, supporting consistency, compliance, and competence across the sector.<br><br>In this blog, <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/dr-richard-dune-blog" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">Dr Richard Dune</span></em></a> explores why the CSTF is vital for healthcare settings, examining its impact, legal underpinnings, and how it fosters a safer, more effective workforce.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-35_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-36_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-37_">What is the Core Skills Training Framework?</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-39_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-b8cd2c64-c077-419f-b49d-8deb5b4fa94b"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The Core Skills Training Framework (CSTF) is a standardised framework outlining the minimum learning outcomes, refresher training intervals, and links to legislation for statutory and mandatory training in healthcare.<br><br>In the context of the CSTF, statutory training is the training required by law to ensure safety and compliance in healthcare workplaces. Mandatory training is the training deemed necessary by healthcare organisations to meet regulatory standards and deliver safe care.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-42_">Why was the CSTF developed?</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-44_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-dcb6a382-dca9-4654-baf5-d13036b6c452"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The CSTF was developed to standardise statutory and mandatory training across the UK’s healthcare sector. It addresses the need for consistency, ensuring that all healthcare workers meet nationally agreed training outcomes regardless of their role or organisation.
</span></p><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-47_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-c45255e8-62cf-4740-b8d9-13c02050b359"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The framework was designed to:</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dhFVuh gFqzWs pf-50_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-51_">Enhance workforce competence.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-53_">Improve patient safety.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-55_">Support compliance with key legislation, such as the Health and Safety at Work Act 1974, the Care Act 2014, and the Equality Act 2010.</li></ul><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-57_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-d2ec572b-739c-48b8-9c4b-9d49de480703"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">By aligning training with CSTF standards, organisations can reduce duplication, improve efficiency, and ensure the portability of training records, fostering a skilled, compliant, and mobile workforce equipped to deliver high-quality, safe care.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-60_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-61_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-62_">What are the benefits of the CSTF?</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-64_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-e5f7d865-7bab-4d94-8a38-26c26f6098df"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The CSTF provides numerous benefits, including:
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dhFVuh gFqzWs pf-67_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-68_"><strong>Standardisation</strong> - Ensures consistent training outcomes across organisations.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-70_"><strong>Compliance</strong> - Supports adherence to legal and regulatory requirements, including <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/blogs/dr-richard-dune/what-is-the-role-of-the-care-quality-commission" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">Care Quality Commission (CQC)</span></em></a> standards.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-72_"><strong>Workforce competence</strong> - Improves staff skills, confidence, and patient safety.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-74_"><strong>Portability </strong>- Training records are recognised across organisations, reducing duplication.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-76_"><strong>Efficiency </strong>- Streamlines training delivery, saving time and resources.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-78_"><strong>Professional development</strong> - Meets revalidation and CPD requirements for healthcare professionals.
