</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-82_"><strong>Flexibility</strong> - Offers tailored training for diverse roles and responsibilities.
</li></ul><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-84_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-bc4e10fe-a9f5-423c-b371-06feab5829ad"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">These benefits collectively enhance safety, compliance, and care quality in the healthcare sector.

